#: src/applib/storage_property_descr_nvme_attribute.cpp:108
msgid ""
"The minimum Composite Temperature field value indicates an overheating "
"condition during which the controller operation continues. Immediate "
"remediation is recommended (e.g. additional cooling or workload reduction)."
msgstr ""
"材料温度域的最小值表示存在过热情况，而在此期间控制器仍在继续运行。建议立即采"
"取补救措施（例如，增加冷却或减少工作负载）。"

#: src/applib/storage_property_descr_nvme_attribute.cpp:112
msgid ""
"The amount of time in minutes that the controller is operational and the "
