#: src/gui/gsc_info_window.cpp:1420
msgid ""
"Short self-test consists of a collection of test routines that have the "
"highest chance of detecting drive problems. Its result is reported in the "
"Self-Test Log. Note that this test is in no way comprehensive. Its main "
"purpose is to detect totally damaged drives without running a full surface "
"scan.\n"
"Note: On some drives this actually runs several consequent tests, which may "
"cause the program to display the test progress incorrectly."
msgstr ""
"简要自测试包含一系列最有可能检测到驱动器问题的测试例程。其结果会在自检日志中"
"报告。请注意，此测试绝非全面测试。其主要目的是在不进行全面表面扫描的情况下检"
"测完全损坏的驱动器。\n"
"注意：在某些硬盘上，此操作实际上会连续运行多个测试，这可能会导致程序错误地显"
"示测试进度。"

#: src/gui/gsc_info_window.cpp:1434
msgid ""
"Extended self-test examines complete disk surface and performs various test "
"routines built into the drive. Its result is reported in the Self-Test Log."
msgstr ""
"详尽自测试会检查整个磁盘表面，并执行内置于硬盘中的各种测试程序。其结果会在自"
"检日志中报告。"

#: src/gui/gsc_info_window.cpp:1444
msgid ""
